{
  "id": "RAW_004265ef",
  "title": "华为开源 7B 多模态模型，视觉定位和 OCR 能力出色，你的昇腾端侧“新甜点”来了",
  "url": "https://www.qbitai.com/2026/01/366548.html",
  "date": "2026-01-05 05:05:39",
  "author": "衡宇",
  "siteName": "量子位",
  "content": "<!--摘要样式-->\n<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p class=\"pgc-h-forward-slash\" data-track=\"27\">允中 发自 凹非寺</p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-h-forward-slash\" data-track=\"28\">量子位 | 公众号 QbitAI</p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-track=\"2\">7B量级模型，向来是端侧部署与个人开发者的心头好。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"3\">轻量化特性让它能灵活适配各类终端场景，而强劲性能又能覆盖图像信息抽取、文档理解、视频解析、物体定位等高频需求。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"4\">刚刚，华为重磅推出<strong>开源新玩家openPangu-VL-7B</strong>，直接瞄准这一核心场景精准发力。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"5\">昇腾原生的模型结构，让openPangu-VL-7B的推理性能极具性价比：</p>\n  <p data-track=\"6\">720P图像在单张Ascend Atlas 800T A2卡上<strong>首字模型推理时延</strong>（ViT与LLM模型时延和）<strong>仅160毫秒</strong>，能够进行5FPS的实时推理；<strong>训练阶段的MFU更是达到42.5%</strong>。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"7\">更值得关注的是，模型<strong>在预训练阶段完成了3T+tokens的无突刺集群长稳训练</strong>，为开发者使用昇腾集群提供了极具价值的实践参考。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/3cb78b33493044e3a44c5d65287be2b8~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20260105130230C1B49F50EF0646F46229&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=dRtL%2FEcN9JjrxSF%2B79DUvc8fQGI%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/3cb78b33493044e3a44c5d65287be2b8~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20260105130230C1B49F50EF0646F46229&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=dRtL%2FEcN9JjrxSF%2B79DUvc8fQGI%3D\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"8\">openPangu-VL-7B<strong>在通用视觉问答、文档图表理解&amp;OCR、视觉定位、短视频理解等核心任务上表现突出</strong>，在开源榜单中力压同量级模型，展现出强悍的综合实力。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/6ef36f02fccb402295e4ebe64470549f~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20260105130230C1B49F50EF0646F46229&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=Bk7jCvOwXtRf18XzjNU39m9Elbk%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/6ef36f02fccb402295e4ebe64470549f~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20260105130230C1B49F50EF0646F46229&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=Bk7jCvOwXtRf18XzjNU39m9Elbk%3D\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"9\">官方提供的cookbook也展现了模型在这些领域的优异能力。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"10\">比如我们给模型一张菜品图，让模型找到一共有多少个樱桃番茄，模型能够点出所有的位置并正确计数。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p26-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/892d4cb0becb4a948fd771a96c2e11d6~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20260105130230C1B49F50EF0646F46229&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=IGKaPTQLmgU0ptDgEieP459Zbx0%3D\" data-src=\"https://p26-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/892d4cb0becb4a948fd771a96c2e11d6~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20260105130230C1B49F50EF0646F46229&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=IGKaPTQLmgU0ptDgEieP459Zbx0%3D\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"11\">给模型一张年报截图，模型也能将其转变为markdown格式，省去了人工摘录的痛苦。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/0ff33927e42e4c68ab04f5e29379221b~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20260105130230C1B49F50EF0646F46229&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=JnAjHl58Fat%2F3PphqWPty%2FixXbQ%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/0ff33927e42e4c68ab04f5e29379221b~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20260105130230C1B49F50EF0646F46229&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=JnAjHl58Fat%2F3PphqWPty%2FixXbQ%3D\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"12\">除了亮眼的榜单成绩和针对昇腾的训推优化，技术报告中<strong>还披露了若干核心技术细节</strong>，揭秘模型高性能背后的设计巧思：</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/8ad1ebe592194b9bb941e82f31659622~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20260105130230C1B49F50EF0646F46229&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=Kcw1up4PYx%2BTifouR9cyx5W0sZc%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/8ad1ebe592194b9bb941e82f31659622~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20260105130230C1B49F50EF0646F46229&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=Kcw1up4PYx%2BTifouR9cyx5W0sZc%3D\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"14\">业界传统视觉编码器多针对GPU架构设计，没有充分发挥昇腾硬件优势。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"15\">团队通过大量先导实验与性能分析，<strong>找到模型结构的最优平衡点</strong>——相同参数量下，该视觉编码器在昇腾芯片上的吞吐较使用窗注意力的ViT-H系列编码器提升15%。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"16\">同时，采用多标签对比学习框架，让模型具备更优的细粒度理解能力，为后续VLM训练中的视觉定位数据学习筑牢基础。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"18\">为解决不同长度训练样本的学习均衡问题，openPangu-VL-7B<strong>创新采用 “加权逐样本损失+逐令牌损失” 的混合训练方案</strong>，加权系数由令牌位置和样本重要性动态决定。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/a6917e8e2baa464dbff82b414f2a22c0~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20260105130230C1B49F50EF0646F46229&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=gD6rcVYNwrjePcUqYJgwYIT%2FtFQ%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/a6917e8e2baa464dbff82b414f2a22c0~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20260105130230C1B49F50EF0646F46229&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=gD6rcVYNwrjePcUqYJgwYIT%2FtFQ%3D\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"19\">这一设计让模型在训练中既能吃透长回复数据，也不忽视短回复信息，避免 “顾此失彼”，消融实验已充分验证其有效性。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/6c10e7bd161941ccb100c055cff6444a~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20260105130230C1B49F50EF0646F46229&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=D%2BnYMitiTa6YdifhOR1AKI3M9ZY%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/6c10e7bd161941ccb100c055cff6444a~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20260105130230C1B49F50EF0646F46229&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=D%2BnYMitiTa6YdifhOR1AKI3M9ZY%3D\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"20\"><strong>3）带填充的定位数据格式</strong></p>\n  <p data-track=\"21\">区别于业界主流的0-999定位方案，openPangu-VL-7B<strong>采用000-999千分位带填充相对坐标完成视觉定位</strong>。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"22\">整齐的三个token进行位置回归，不仅降低了模型学习难度，更显著提升了格式遵从性，让定位任务的精度和效率同步提升。</p>\n  <div class=\"pgc-img\">\n   <p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"syl-page-img\" src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/a5d7a4eff68b409ea45cbe6a4a14c13d~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20260105130230C1B49F50EF0646F46229&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=QT2HyG%2BMei%2BG%2Bu9D3yX31WAZzPw%3D\" data-src=\"https://p3-sign.toutiaoimg.com/tos-cn-i-6w9my0ksvp/a5d7a4eff68b409ea45cbe6a4a14c13d~tplv-tt-shrink:640:0.image?lk3s=06827d14&amp;traceid=20260105130230C1B49F50EF0646F46229&amp;x-expires=2147483647&amp;x-signature=QT2HyG%2BMei%2BG%2Bu9D3yX31WAZzPw%3D\"></p>\n   <p class=\"pgc-img-caption\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-track=\"23\">此外，技术报告还深入探索了预训练数据配比、位置编码、模型融合等关键策略，<strong>为开发者提供了全面的技术细节参考</strong>。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"24\">对于昇腾使用者而言，openPangu-VL-7B 的开源无疑是一大利好。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"25\">这款兼具轻量化、高性能与强通用性的多模态模型，既为端侧开发和个人使用提供了新选择，也将进一步丰富昇腾生态的应用场景，为创新注入新动力。</p>\n  <p data-track=\"26\">模型链接：\n   <br class=\"sysbr\">\n   https://ai.gitcode.com/ascend-tribe/openPangu-VL-7B\n   <br class=\"sysbr\">\n   技术报告：\n   <br class=\"sysbr\">\n   https://ai.gitcode.com/ascend-tribe/openPangu-VL-7B/blob/main/doc/technical_report.pdf</p>\n  <!--版权声明-->\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "华为开源 7B 多模态模型 openPangu-VL-7B，专为昇腾端侧优化，在视觉定位、OCR 和多模态理解任务上表现出色，并提供了核心技术细节。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "华为开源 7B 多模态模型 openPangu-VL-7B，专为昇腾端侧优化，在视觉定位、OCR 和多模态理解任务上表现出色，并提供了核心技术细节。",
  "summary": "华为正式开源了其 7B 量级多模态模型 openPangu-VL-7B，该模型专为端侧部署和个人开发者设计，特别优化了在昇腾硬件上的性能。文章详细介绍了 openPangu-VL-7B 在 720P 图像推理上仅 160 毫秒的首字时延，支持 5FPS 实时推理，训练阶段 MFU 达到 42.5%的优异表现。该模型在通用视觉问答、文档/图表理解、OCR、视觉定位和短视频理解等任务上表现出色，甚至在公开榜单上超越同量级模型。文章深入探讨了其核心技术细节，包括针对昇腾架构优化的视觉编码器、创新的混合训练方案（加权逐样本损失+逐令牌损失），以及带有填充功能 000-999 千分位相对坐标的定位数据格式。这些技术创新显著提升了模型在昇腾芯片上的吞吐量、细粒度理解能力以及视觉定位精度和效率。openPangu-VL-7B 的开源为昇腾生态带来了高性能、轻量化的多模态解决方案，具有重要的实践参考价值。",
